what is the thing that brings us
the most joy, the most passion,

00:29:12.010 --> 00:29:15.880 align:middle line:84%
the most excitement for life,
because that is going to fuel

00:29:15.880 --> 00:29:19.930 align:middle line:84%
our actions when we go
