important thing today

00:37:38.280 --> 00:37:40.350 align:middle line:84%
because people are trying
to do so many things.

00:37:40.350 --> 00:37:42.720 align:middle line:84%
Transition meditation
means, OK, let's say

00:37:42.720 --> 00:37:45.300 align:middle line:84%
