got to check my inbox,

00:37:45.300 --> 00:37:47.730 align:middle line:84%
and then I have to
create a presentation.

00:37:47.730 --> 00:37:50.910 align:middle line:10%
Well, I don't just do my
email and then jump in

00:37:50.910 --> 00:37:52.260 align:middle line:10%
and start creating that.

00:37:52.260 --> 00:37:55.350 align:middle line:84%
Instead, as soon as I'm done
with the email, I get up,

00:37:55.350 --> 00:37:57.110 align:middle line:84%
