if you're a dad or you're a mom

00:38:07.040 --> 00:38:09.600 align:middle line:84%
and you're coming home from
work and your spouse or the kids

00:38:09.600 --> 00:38:12.470 align:middle line:84%
are in the house, don't take
that long commute where you're

00:38:12.470 --> 00:38:15.095 align:middle line:84%
