off for a minute.

00:38:23.860 --> 00:38:28.980 align:middle line:84%
Take a five, 10, 15-minute
meditation, then get up ,

00:38:28.980 --> 00:38:30.960 align:middle line:90%
then go into the house.

00:38:30.960 --> 00:38:34.170 align:middle line:10%
That transition from the
commute to going into the house

00:38:34.170 --> 00:38:37.950 align:middle line:10%
gives you time to reset,
to have some intention,

00:38:37.950 --> 00:38:41.070 align:middle line:10%
and to go in the house as
a better mom, better dad,

00:38:41.070 --> 00:38:43.860 align:middle line:10%
a better caregiver, a better
lover, because if we just

00:38:43.860 --> 00:38:45.800 align:middle line:10%
keep going from one thing to
another thing to another thing,

00:38:45.800 --> 00:38:47.925 align:middle line:10%
to another thing, another
thing, not only does that

00:38:47.925 --> 00:38:50.280 align:middle line:10%
lead to burnout, it
makes us miss life.

00:38:50.280 --> 00:38:52.050 align:middle line:84%
It makes us lack
the ability to bring

00:38:52.050 --> 00:38:53.950 align:middle line:90%
good energy into a moment.

00:38:53.950 --> 00:38:57.000 align:middle line:84%
And so I tell people, find your
moments in between everything.

00:38:57.000 --> 00:38:59.940 align:middle line:84%
There is nothing-- if I
have a full day of calls

00:38:59.940 --> 00:39:01.513 align:middle line:84%
and then I gotta
go meet my wife,

00:39:01.513 --> 00:39:03.180 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to meditate
between those two.

00:39:03.180 --> 00:39:05.160 align:middle line:84%
I have to, otherwise
she's going to get Brendan

00:39:05.160 --> 00:39:06.323 align:middle line:90%
who just did the calls guy.

00:39:06.323 --> 00:39:07.740 align:middle line:84%
I don't want her
to have that guy.

00:39:07.740 --> 00:39:09.240 align:middle line:90%
I want her to have her husband.

00:39:09.240 --> 00:39:10.823 align:middle line:84%
And the only way I
can show up for her

00:39:10.823 --> 00:39:13.140 align:middle line:90%
is a transition meditation.

00:39:13.140 --> 00:39:16.350 align:middle line:84%
>> And as a human being
who is very driven,

00:39:16.350 --> 00:39:19.230 align:middle line:84%
who is very type A, who
works and puts effort

00:39:19.230 --> 00:39:22.530 align:middle line:84%
into everything, it's a really
wonderful counterbalance.

00:39:22.530 --> 00:39:25.140 align:middle line:84%
And I also loved that
it's not necessarily

00:39:25.140 --> 00:39:28.500 align:middle line:84%
attached to any
particular religion

00:39:28.500 --> 00:39:30.600 align:middle line:84%
and that it's really
open for all of us.

00:39:30.600 --> 00:39:33.270 align:middle line:90%


00:39:33.270 --> 00:39:39.015 align:middle line:84%
I found that I can use all of my
type A, driven, get-it-doneness

00:39:39.015 --> 00:39:41.490 align:middle line:84%
in the rest of my life
and have this really

00:39:41.490 --> 00:39:44.460 align:middle line:84%
beautiful, simple,
straightforward practice

00:39:44.460 --> 00:39:48.990 align:middle line:84%
to help me dip down into
this infinite intelligence,

00:39:48.990 --> 00:39:52.380 align:middle line:84%
this cosmic consciousness
that I think many of us

00:39:52.380 --> 00:39:55.980 align:middle line:84%
have experienced or felt at
different times in our life,

00:39:55.980 --> 00:39:58.740 align:middle line:84%
whether we're with a loved
one or we're witnessing

00:39:58.740 --> 00:40:02.790 align:middle line:84%
the beauty of a flower or
even in profound sadness when

00:40:02.790 --> 00:40:05.940 align:middle line:84%
we feel this level of
connection of oneness

00:40:05.940 --> 00:40:08.050 align:middle line:90%
with everyone and everything.

00:40:08.050 --> 00:40:10.410 align:middle line:84%
And when I come out
of my meditation,

00:40:10.410 --> 00:40:16.830 align:middle line:84%
I find myself feeling a
level of energy and charge

00:40:16.830 --> 00:40:18.870 align:middle line:84%
that, frankly, I haven't
been able to access

00:40:18.870 --> 00:40:20.610 align:middle line:90%
through any other method.

00:40:20.610 --> 00:40:25.020 align:middle line:84%
>> You have to be an active,
consistent meditator.

00:40:25.020 --> 00:40:28.020 align:middle line:84%
Meditation is
absolutely crucial.

00:40:28.020 --> 00:40:30.780 align:middle line:84%
It allows you to gain the
upper hand and the control

00:40:30.780 --> 00:40:33.560 align:middle line:84%
over that thinking brain
and that idle chatter

00:40:33.560 --> 00:40:35.910 align:middle line:84%
and allows you to
be fully immersed

00:40:35.910 --> 00:40:37.330 align:middle line:90%
in that present moment.

00:40:37.330 --> 00:40:41.370 align:middle line:90%
And as an athlete, that's key.

00:40:41.370 --> 00:40:44.640 align:middle line:84%
You can't enter that flow
state that you hear about

00:40:44.640 --> 00:40:46.410 align:middle line:90%
if you're entertaining thought.

00:40:46.410 --> 00:40:50.100 align:middle line:84%
You have to be fully present
in what you're doing.

00:40:50.100 --> 00:40:54.360 align:middle line:84%
And what happens when you
are consistently meditating

00:40:54.360 --> 00:40:56.640 align:middle line:90%
is that you develop this acumen.

00:40:56.640 --> 00:40:59.310 align:middle line:84%
It's like push-ups
for the brain.

00:40:59.310 --> 00:41:01.980 align:middle line:84%
And you then are the
master of the brain

00:41:01.980 --> 00:41:03.763 align:middle line:90%
rather than being its slave.

00:41:03.763 --> 00:41:15.840 align:middle line:90%


00:41:15.840 --> 00:41:18.090 align:middle line:84%
>> When you meditate, you
go into this brainwave state

00:41:18.090 --> 00:41:19.230 align:middle line:90%
called alpha.

00:41:19.230 --> 00:41:22.440 align:middle line:84%
Alpha state is the state
of a relaxed awareness,

00:41:22.440 --> 00:41:24.690 align:middle line:84%
and relaxed awareness is
where you can train yourself,

00:41:24.690 --> 00:41:26.530 align:middle line:84%
actually, to learn
a language faster,

00:41:26.530 --> 00:41:29.370 align:middle line:84%
to be able to learn rapidly
because your conscious mind is

00:41:29.370 --> 00:41:32.410 align:middle line:84%
actually set aside and you
just absorb information faster.

00:41:32.410 --> 00:41:36.330 align:middle line:84%
>> And we can see the brain
opens in so many new areas when

00:41:36.330 --> 00:41:39.960 align:middle line:84%
we reach that state, meaning
that you tap into different

00:41:39.960 --> 00:41:42.863 align:middle line:84%
things that were not
accessible before.

00:41:42.863 --> 00:41:44.280 align:middle line:84%
And when you then
start to connect

00:41:44.280 --> 00:41:48.000 align:middle line:84%
those areas and those thoughts
and basically that network

00:41:48.000 --> 00:41:53.130 align:middle line:84%
of trillions of nerve cells,
you can develop intuition.

00:41:53.130 --> 00:41:55.080 align:middle line:84%
>> Intuition is just
our internal wisdom.

00:41:55.080 --> 00:41:57.870 align:middle line:84%
It's this natural knowing
that each of us have

00:41:57.870 --> 00:42:00.060 align:middle line:84%
that oftentimes we're
never listening to.

00:42:00.060 --> 00:42:02.730 align:middle line:84%
One of the benefits that I
had was my mom trained me ever

00:42:02.730 --> 00:42:06.355 align:middle line:84%
since I was little to listen to
the still, small voice inside.

00:42:06.355 --> 00:42:07.980 align:middle line:84%
And she said, you
know, you will always

00:42:07.980 --> 00:42:11.550 align:middle line:84%
know the right move to make if
you tap inside and you listen.

00:42:11.550 --> 00:42:12.850 align:middle line:90%
There will always be an answer.

00:42:12.850 --> 00:42:15.460 align:middle line:84%
So I heard this message
over and over again.

00:42:15.460 --> 00:42:19.350 align:middle line:84%
So whenever in my adult life
I'm wondering which way to go,

00:42:19.350 --> 00:42:22.110 align:middle line:84%
I get quiet and I pay
attention to what's

00:42:22.110 --> 00:42:25.342 align:middle line:90%
happening on the inside.

00:42:25.342 --> 00:42:27.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Intuition is something that's
been undervalued for many,

00:42:27.800 --> 00:42:28.220 align:middle line:90%
many years.

00:42:28.220 --> 00:42:30.720 align:middle line:84%
I think people are starting to
really appreciate and respect

00:42:30.720 --> 00:42:34.645 align:middle line:84%
the fact that it has
huge value and not

00:42:34.645 --> 00:42:35.770 align:middle line:90%
just in our personal lives.

00:42:35.770 --> 00:42:37.060 align:middle line:84%
People think of an
intuition as just,

00:42:37.060 --> 00:42:39.340 align:middle line:84%
oh, it's some fluffy, kind
of personal concept thing,

00:42:39.340 --> 00:42:40.990 align:middle line:84%
and it just works
in my personal life.

00:42:40.990 --> 00:42:43.480 align:middle line:84%
It's got a massive
application in business.

00:42:43.480 --> 00:42:45.700 align:middle line:84%
How many of us have
got into relationships

00:42:45.700 --> 00:42:49.850 align:middle line:84%
that we know in our heart and
soul, we know it's not aligned,

00:42:49.850 --> 00:42:52.700 align:middle line:84%
whether it's in business or
it's in a personal relationship?

00:42:52.700 --> 00:42:55.240 align:middle line:84%
We do it anyway,
and it goes south.

00:42:55.240 --> 00:42:56.693 align:middle line:90%
We get screwed eventually.

00:42:56.693 --> 00:42:59.110 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes we blame the
person, sometimes we get angry.

00:42:59.110 --> 00:43:00.777 align:middle line:84%
But if we looked in
the mirror and said,

00:43:00.777 --> 00:43:05.100 align:middle line:84%
OK, did you really know that
that was in alignment or not,

00:43:05.100 --> 00:43:07.850 align:middle line:84%
and often the case
is we absolutely did.

00:43:07.850 --> 00:43:10.510 align:middle line:84%
And I think sometimes we're
absorbing so much information

00:43:10.510 --> 00:43:13.480 align:middle line:84%
that we're not giving it
time to go from information

00:43:13.480 --> 00:43:16.300 align:middle line:84%
to knowledge, knowledge
to wisdom, and wisdom

00:43:16.300 --> 00:43:19.270 align:middle line:84%
to awareness because
I'm too busy running

00:43:19.270 --> 00:43:21.900 align:middle line:84%
to the next book and the
next book and the next book.

00:43:21.900 --> 00:43:23.680 align:middle line:84%
I'm absorbing so
much information,

00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:26.440 align:middle line:84%
but I'm not allowing it to
translate into awareness

00:43:26.440 --> 00:43:27.428 align:middle line:90%
and understanding.

00:43:27.428 --> 00:43:29.470 align:middle line:84%
So to me, intuition is
one of these things that's

00:43:29.470 --> 00:43:32.780 align:middle line:84%
been suppressed,
it's been blocked,

00:43:32.780 --> 00:43:35.170 align:middle line:84%
and I would encourage
anybody in the world,

00:43:35.170 --> 00:43:37.690 align:middle line:84%
if they want it, if they want
to get in touch with more

00:43:37.690 --> 00:43:40.690 align:middle line:84%
intuition, if they want to
increase their intuition,

00:43:40.690 --> 00:43:44.812 align:middle line:84%
if they want to
uncover more of it,

00:43:44.812 --> 00:43:46.270 align:middle line:84%
don't go looking
for it externally.

00:43:46.270 --> 00:43:48.710 align:middle line:90%
Ask yourself, why isn't it?

00:43:48.710 --> 00:43:49.960 align:middle line:90%
Why am I not in touch with it?

00:43:49.960 --> 00:43:51.267 align:middle line:90%
What's blocking it?

00:43:51.267 --> 00:43:52.600 align:middle line:90%
Intuition has just been blocked.

00:43:52.600 --> 00:43:53.860 align:middle line:90%
It's already there.

00:43:53.860 --> 00:43:56.340 align:middle line:90%
We all have it.

00:43:56.340 --> 00:44:01.050 align:middle line:84%
>> I believe that there is a
tremendous amount of guidance

00:44:01.050 --> 00:44:03.420 align:middle line:84%
that I don't see
with my physical eye.

00:44:03.420 --> 00:44:06.000 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that
my primary job

00:44:06.000 --> 00:44:09.840 align:middle line:84%
is to just be in alignment
with that source.

00:44:09.840 --> 00:44:12.510 align:middle line:84%
And as I align, I can
hear that guidance.

00:44:12.510 --> 00:44:15.240 align:middle line:84%
I can allow that guidance
to show up in my life,

00:44:15.240 --> 00:44:19.650 align:middle line:84%
open invisible doors, write
through me, speak through me,

00:44:19.650 --> 00:44:22.860 align:middle line:84%
just move through me
in magnificent ways.

00:44:22.860 --> 00:44:24.510 align:middle line:84%
And trust me, there's
plenty of things

00:44:24.510 --> 00:44:26.920 align:middle line:84%
I get hung up about, things
that are out of my control,

00:44:26.920 --> 00:44:29.820 align:middle line:84%
but I continue to come back
to that space of surrender

00:44:29.820 --> 00:44:34.740 align:middle line:84%
because, as a human, I'm having
a human experience of wanting

00:44:34.740 --> 00:44:40.020 align:middle line:84%
and trying to control timing of
things that are completely out

00:44:40.020 --> 00:44:41.050 align:middle line:90%
of my hands.

00:44:41.050 --> 00:44:46.140 align:middle line:84%
But those are momentary lapses,
and I've transformed that fear

00:44:46.140 --> 00:44:49.290 align:middle line:84%
into faith, and I've
chosen to allow that faith

00:44:49.290 --> 00:44:50.890 align:middle line:90%
muscle to be stronger.

00:44:50.890 --> 00:44:55.050 align:middle line:84%
So it's not that I measure
my spiritual success based

00:44:55.050 --> 00:44:57.323 align:middle line:90%
on how perfectly aligned I am.

00:44:57.323 --> 00:44:59.490 align:middle line:84%
I really measure it based
on how quickly I come back

00:44:59.490 --> 00:45:00.581 align:middle line:90%
to alignment.

00:45:00.581 --> 00:45:04.730 align:middle line:90%


00:45:04.730 --> 00:45:06.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Take care of yourself.

00:45:06.310 --> 00:45:10.330 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people go hard at their
career, go hard at parenting,

00:45:10.330 --> 00:45:12.250 align:middle line:84%
and without taking
care of yourself,

00:45:12.250 --> 00:45:14.080 align:middle line:84%
you really can't
take care of others.

00:45:14.080 --> 00:45:16.160 align:middle line:84%
The more you take
care of yourself,

00:45:16.160 --> 00:45:19.390 align:middle line:84%
the more energy you're going
to have to pour into others.

00:45:19.390 --> 00:45:22.100 align:middle line:84%
Fill your cup and then serve
others from the overflow.

00:45:22.100 --> 00:45:25.550 align:middle line:84%
That's something one of my
favorite speakers always says.

00:45:25.550 --> 00:45:26.350 align:middle line:90%
It's Lisa Nichols.

00:45:26.350 --> 00:45:29.260 align:middle line:84%
She's just like, you're supposed
to serve from your saucer.

00:45:29.260 --> 00:45:33.000 align:middle line:90%


00:45:33.000 --> 00:45:35.100 align:middle line:84%
Meditation and yoga,
all that together was

00:45:35.100 --> 00:45:36.450 align:middle line:90%
making me a stronger person.

00:45:36.450 --> 00:45:39.120 align:middle line:84%
Every day, I felt
stronger and stronger.

00:45:39.120 --> 00:45:41.730 align:middle line:84%
Some of the things that I
experienced when I was younger,

00:45:41.730 --> 00:45:44.750 align:middle line:84%
I started to release and
let go through practicing

00:45:44.750 --> 00:45:45.690 align:middle line:90%
more and more yoga.

00:45:45.690 --> 00:45:48.360 align:middle line:84%
And it's like, the more
yoga that I practiced,

00:45:48.360 --> 00:45:51.060 align:middle line:84%
the more I was able
to release the past

00:45:51.060 --> 00:45:54.810 align:middle line:84%
and step into my strength
as a person, as a teacher,

00:45:54.810 --> 00:45:57.330 align:middle line:90%
and as a leader.

00:45:57.330 --> 00:46:00.960 align:middle line:84%
>> Pay attention to that
little voice there and bring

00:46:00.960 --> 00:46:05.700 align:middle line:84%
expression to that in your
own life and, in so doing,

00:46:05.700 --> 00:46:11.880 align:middle line:84%
to perhaps connect with yourself
more deeply and ultimately

00:46:11.880 --> 00:46:14.790 align:middle line:84%
express a more authentic
version of who you are.

00:46:14.790 --> 00:46:17.650 align:middle line:90%


00:46:17.650 --> 00:46:21.970 align:middle line:84%
>> We're all interconnected,
and to contribute your utmost

00:46:21.970 --> 00:46:26.680 align:middle line:84%
to society, to humanity, I think
you need to pursue what it is

00:46:26.680 --> 00:46:28.090 align:middle line:90%
that's uniquely within you.

00:46:28.090 --> 00:46:31.135 align:middle line:84%
And I just think that that is
the best course for humanity.

00:46:31.135 --> 00:46:33.010 align:middle line:84%
If everyone was to do
that, I think the world

00:46:33.010 --> 00:46:34.052 align:middle line:90%
would be a happier place.

00:46:34.052 --> 00:46:42.790 align:middle line:90%


00:46:42.790 --> 00:46:47.500 align:middle line:84%
>> I think that we are all,
all of us without exception,

00:46:47.500 --> 00:46:52.480 align:middle line:84%
sitting on top of mountains of
untapped human potential just

00:46:52.480 --> 00:46:55.870 align:middle line:84%
waiting to be unlocked
and unleashed.

00:46:55.870 --> 00:46:59.290 align:middle line:84%
And I was lucky enough
to wake up at 40

00:46:59.290 --> 00:47:02.320 align:middle line:90%
and embark upon this journey.

00:47:02.320 --> 00:47:05.800 align:middle line:84%
And my responsibility
with what I've experienced

00:47:05.800 --> 00:47:08.740 align:middle line:84%
is to share with
others in hopes that I

00:47:08.740 --> 00:47:11.680 align:middle line:84%
can help to activate and
catalyze their version of what

00:47:11.680 --> 00:47:12.550 align:middle line:90%
I've experienced.

00:47:12.550 --> 00:47:16.180 align:middle line:84%
Of course, not everyone wants to
be an ultra endurance athlete.

00:47:16.180 --> 00:47:17.830 align:middle line:90%
It's not about that.

00:47:17.830 --> 00:47:20.620 align:middle line:84%
My hope is that people can
look at those experiences

00:47:20.620 --> 00:47:23.350 align:middle line:84%
and my story and
draw inspiration

00:47:23.350 --> 00:47:28.660 align:middle line:84%
from that to then examine their
own lives under a microscope

00:47:28.660 --> 00:47:33.700 align:middle line:84%
to better identify what
it is within them that has

00:47:33.700 --> 00:47:37.970 align:middle line:90%
gone unaddressed for too long.

00:47:37.970 --> 00:47:40.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Your dreams matter
because you matter.

00:47:40.930 --> 00:47:42.918 align:middle line:84%
So follow your
dreams because that's

00:47:42.918 --> 00:47:44.710 align:middle line:84%
the thing that brings
us the most joy, when

00:47:44.710 --> 00:47:47.100 align:middle line:84%
we have something
to look forward to,

00:47:47.100 --> 00:47:49.810 align:middle line:84%
when we have something
we want to chase.

00:47:49.810 --> 00:47:53.260 align:middle line:84%
It gives us a purpose,
a reason, and a meaning

00:47:53.260 --> 00:47:58.410 align:middle line:84%
to get up every single
day and make a difference.

00:47:58.410 --> 00:48:02.140 align:middle line:84%
>> What is it about you
that makes you uniquely you?

00:48:02.140 --> 00:48:03.765 align:middle line:84%
What gets you out of
bed in the morning

00:48:03.765 --> 00:48:06.240 align:middle line:90%
and excited about your life?

00:48:06.240 --> 00:48:09.140 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not suspecting
that everybody's

00:48:09.140 --> 00:48:11.340 align:middle line:84%
going to have an answer
to that immediately,

00:48:11.340 --> 00:48:14.760 align:middle line:84%
but I think exploration
of that inquiry

00:48:14.760 --> 00:48:17.820 align:middle line:84%
is the path forward
to ultimately living

00:48:17.820 --> 00:48:19.590 align:middle line:84%
a more purposeful,
meaningful life,

00:48:19.590 --> 00:48:22.410 align:middle line:84%
because if you can
identify that thing--

00:48:22.410 --> 00:48:27.360 align:middle line:84%
and it can be as silly as I
like making paper-mache birds,

00:48:27.360 --> 00:48:29.670 align:middle line:84%
or I want to tell
jokes on stage,

00:48:29.670 --> 00:48:32.400 align:middle line:84%
or I want to learn how
to play the guitar.

00:48:32.400 --> 00:48:35.310 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't have to be
that thing of like, well,

00:48:35.310 --> 00:48:38.230 align:middle line:84%
I'm just going to
quit my job overnight.

00:48:38.230 --> 00:48:40.140 align:middle line:84%
But I think the more
you can invest yourself

00:48:40.140 --> 00:48:42.930 align:middle line:84%
in that journey of
trying to identify

00:48:42.930 --> 00:48:48.590 align:middle line:84%
what it is that you are here to
